512
01:40:32,391 --> 01:40:35,311
Sad živim u Americi!

513
01:40:54,393 --> 01:41:00,649
Evo. -Ne, hvala. Nisam
gladan. Želim da ti dam ovo.

514
01:41:05,758 --> 01:41:08,157
